"title": "8702: agnosticism",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8702",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The inability to decide whether or not God exists. It is characterised by indecision and compromise when faced with the challenge to wholehearted commitment, and is condemned as sinful, inexcusable and unnecessary in the light of God's clear self-revelation.</p>\n<h2>Agnosticism is inexcusable in the light of God's self-revelation</h2>\n<h3>In the creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:19-Rom1:20\">ROM 1:19–1:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:1-Ps19:2\">PSA 19:1–19:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:17\">ACT 14:17</a></p>\n<h3>In the person of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:18\">JHN 1:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:9\">JHN 14:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:1-Heb1:3\">HEB 1:1–1:3</a></p>\n<h2>Agnosticism is sinful</h2>\n<h3>Because God calls for wholehearted commitment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:14-Josh24:15\">JOS 24:14–24:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:26\">EXO 32:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:13-Deut6:14\">DEU 6:13–6:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:15-Deut30:19\">DEU 30:15–30:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:15\">ACT 14:15</a></p>\n<h3>Because God's call demands total obedience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:9\">MAT 9:9</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:14\">MRK 2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:27-Luke5:28\">LUK 5:27–5:28</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:18-Matt4:22\">MAT 4:18–4:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:16-Mark1:20\">MRK 1:16–1:20</a></p>\n<h2>Agnosticism results in compromise</h2>\n<h3>In worship</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:21\">1KI 18:21</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:41\">2KI 17:41</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:29-2Kgs17:33\">2KI 17:29–17:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:21\">1CO 10:21</a></p>\n<h3>In commitment</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:24\">MAT 6:24</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:13\">LUK 16:13</a> <em>in the attitude to money</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:19-Matt8:22\">MAT 8:19–8:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:57-Luke9:62\">LUK 9:57–9:62</a> <em>in service</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:14\">2CO 6:14</a> <em>in relationships with unbelievers</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:14\">EPH 4:14</a> <em>in accommodating false teaching</em></p>\n<h2>Agnosticism as a result of ignorance</h2>\n<h3>Ignorance through being uninformed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:23-Acts17:30\">ACT 17:23–17:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:17-Acts3:18\">ACT 3:17–3:18</a></p>\n<h3>Foolish ignorance of God's existence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:1\">PSA 14:1</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps53:1\">PSA 53:1</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps92:5-Ps92:7\">PSA 92:5–92:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:4\">JER 5:4</a></p>\n<h3>Ignorance of God's presence</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:2\">PSA 115:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:3\">PSA 42:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:17\">JOL 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic7:10\">MIC 7:10</a></p>\n<h3>Ignorance as a result of rejecting God's truth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:4\">PSA 10:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps36:1\">PSA 36:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer5:21-Jer5:24\">JER 5:21–5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:11-Zech7:12\">ZEC 7:11–7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:22-Acts2:23\">ACT 2:22–2:23</a></p>\n<h3>Ignorance as a result of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:17-Eph4:19\">EPH 4:17–4:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:3-Isa1:4\">ISA 1:3–1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer4:22\">JER 4:22</a></p>\n<h3>Ignorance is no defence against God's judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18\">ROM 1:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:10-Judg2:14\">JDG 2:10–2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:9-Isa44:11\">ISA 44:9–44:11</a></p>",
